}
<div class="sub-page  AlignH ">
   
    <a class="scrollable-browse scrollable-next"></a> <a class="scrollable-browse scrollable-prev"></a>
    <div  class="title"><h1>@ViewBag.Title</h1></div>
   
    <div id="scrollable" class="scrollable" >
    <div class="items">
                     
            <div class="page-content">
                <div class="content_scrollable_wrap">
                    <figcaption style="height:580px;">
                    <p>My  Account is a free service to all Telstra customers that provides access to a  range of useful online services to help them manage their Telstra services from  their computer or compatible mobile devices. </p>
                    <br /><p>Once  logged in to My Account, customers can perform various account management  functions such as: monitoring calls and data usage, automating payments and  viewing bills online.</p>
                     <br /><p>Customers  can access the Desktop version of My Account through <a href="https://www.my.telstra.com.au/myaccount/home">telstra.com/</a><a href="https://www.my.telstra.com.au/myaccount/home">myaccount</a> (to  log-in) <a href="https://www.my.telstra.com.au/myaccount/register">telstra.com.au/</a><a href="https://www.my.telstra.com.au/myaccount/register">myaccount</a><a href="https://www.my.telstra.com.au/myaccount/register">/register</a> (to  register).</p>
                     <br /><p>Register  customers through Assisted Registration Tool (search for ART in KnowHow) if  they are having difficulty signing up.</p>
                     <br /><p>Customers  can also choose from a range of Telstra24x7 social and mobile Apps to access  their Telstra services on the go.</p>
                </figcaption>

                </div>
            
            </div> @*end item here*@
            
