                        <p>Registration  is fast and simple, customers are required to have:</p>
                        <ul>
                        <li>Telstra  account number <strong>OR </strong>their Telstra Pre-Paid mobile number</li>
                        <li>an  active email address</li>
                         </ul><br />
                        <p>Customers  can chat online to a consultant to promptly receive their account number or  address queries during the registration process</p>
                    </figcaption>
                </div>
